  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You decide to expand upon your already expansive arsenal.</p><p> You add a third weapon, or your Slayer's Rifle if you possess it, to your Trick Weapon.</p><p> This becomes known as the Trick Weapon's Surprise Form.</p><p> This form counts as your Trick Weapon's, Trick Form, for the purposes of interactions with Lunar Slayer features.</p><p> When you first take this trick, choose between the Righteous property or Serrated property.</p><p> Your Trick Weapon's Surprise Form gains this property.</p><p></p>",
